Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会疼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手术做完才两天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两天？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么动不了了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道 问医生吧
