Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:21.53,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}你用双耳 独自聆听着什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:34.38,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我的眼睛 映照出久远的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.59,0:01:37.73,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}选择什么 放弃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.75,0:01:40.94,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我如何能 自行定夺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:44.15,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}选取之物 早已在心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:47.08,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}向神问询 是否有误
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.18,0:01:50.20,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}其实不曾孤独过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.37,0:01:52.75,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}其实一直在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:59.82,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}现在 伸出手去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:03.06,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}已经无所畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:06.57,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}哪怕化身怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.61,0:02:14.65,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我一定 会做到
