Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有宇同学 还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目时同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 阻止崩毁的方案看来有效呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.13,0:02:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算啥方案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处理一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么处理一下…打完针都没止血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是医生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…到底发生了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么成了这副模样？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友利呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友利她没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 她也在这住院
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了熊耳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:02:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.43,0:03:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就知道用能力保护自己！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初 说要用时光回溯能力赌一把的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是你吗 你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:12.21,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 熊耳他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人似乎不想要时光回溯能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想用人质来遏制崩毁能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都算错了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别责备自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事 以后还会发生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少这次的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经让前泊用能力消除了记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但说不准还会有什么人 突然盯上你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你能醒来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直轮流守着你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我还有话想问
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥怎么没来？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 让我揍他几拳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你哥哥心里 熊耳是最好的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 请进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 步未
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 你还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不动就没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 听说右眼看不见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说 那是场会让人送命的大事故
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能活下来就谢天谢地了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复健之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日常生活好像不会受太大影响
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在机构里过得好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很亲切 我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 隼哥哥很没精神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好担心他的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾眼睁睁看着步未过世
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哥哥来说 熊耳就像步未一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我死于这次事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步未会怎么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 请进
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你伤的 比我想象的还要厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给受伤的乙坂同学 带来了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保温便当盒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面 装着什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这味道…难道是！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们共同的回忆 牛舌咖喱！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 居然能在这种地方重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来喂你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我想起了校园生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 这就是我们的青春！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多 尽情吃到厌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 友利还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的伤比你轻得多 快能出院了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了很多大事是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请早日和友利同学一起回学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在和柚咲琳二人世界 感觉也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 请进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:07:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来探病啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！…好险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑羽啊 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…做了点东西来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…难道是奶油浓汤？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 猜对了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲琳亲手制作的奶油浓汤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有补气养元的功效 是黑羽家之宝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论治病还是疗伤 效果都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天送奶油浓汤 原来怀着这番好意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那请张嘴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了就有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种场面 可不能让高城看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美砂 你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 找我这死人干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想问问 人死了会去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像个气球一样 被柚咲牵在手里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等柚咲的能力消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个气球 马上就会飞远
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 趁现在去见见你看重的人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？咋突然说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…差点就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种随时都会消失的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能见的时候 就去见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经死过一次了 你说的我也能懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 以前我经常吃这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是老妈的拿手菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲学了来 总是做给我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我家一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和柚咲不同 是个不孝女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:08:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 早死是我最不孝的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去见见父母吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在能力消失前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会考虑一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 我又睡着了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想问问 你父母是做什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在长野县的深山里做手工荞麦面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我建议你近期去见见他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 时间紧迫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去和经纪人说说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确…需要适应一段时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「接近最后的晚餐」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简称「接餐」！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:57.47,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是最后的晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:59.45,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有点接近那种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.07,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本节目将为您推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.14,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艺人钟爱的「接餐」美食
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还在做这种节目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要介绍的 正是我柚咲琳的「接餐」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这家店
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:12.38,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家店其实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:15.63,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柚咲琳父母开的荞麦面店
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:17.38,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违的亲子重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:19.31,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们看起来很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这丫头 趁着工作的机会去见父母了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是手工荞麦面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与野生蔬菜的天妇罗套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从荞麦面开吃喽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在加足佐料的面汤里 蘸一蘸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是艾草的天妇罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也好好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会说「好吃」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然也能被选作美食节目的主持人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 味道很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太普通了…和便利店一个水平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:11:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 美砂？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 里面有父母的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份佐料 让料理变成了极品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…才会这么好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…我想起了美砂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那丫头 说话做事都不上路子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但依然是个好女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是尽了份孝心啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTB----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 请进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好的说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵锵！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日…快乐的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:12:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是有宇哥哥的十六岁生日的说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下绝不会忘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢 就难得努力一把
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:09.24,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs62\an8\fad(0,0)}（十六岁生日快乐）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:10.87,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs62\an8\fad(300,0)}（可喜可贺）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.74,0:12:12.79,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs62\an8\fad(300,0)}（会有好运）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…是否愿意品尝呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便有劳阁下张口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复健中的人可不能勉强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然甜…但很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是一样的味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是美砂说的「佐料」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:52.60,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:53.42,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:54.40,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来再来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:55.19,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:56.04,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来 再来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.19,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃好吃好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:57.81,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:12:58.43,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会说「好吃」的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没资格说别人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜康复
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完全康复呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你一直在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说句话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这所医院很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察不会来过问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那时的我…一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国外的恐怖组织已经群起发难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就会波及日本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳也不在了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后…我们会怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友利？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛这么惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…来得这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比你先出院 想来找你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听你哥哥说什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说日本很快就会被卷入外国的恐怖袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥失魂落魄 好像变了个人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后或许会有许多危险人物打我的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再失去任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再让人变得不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果凭我的力量能做些什么就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想不出办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友利 我该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办法 倒是有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:15:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥的研究设施
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经研制出疫苗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在下次彗星到来时防止能力者出现 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你夺走世上现存的所有能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再夺走从现在开始显现的能力 就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 也有风险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你获得上千 上万个能力之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕会变成有能力毁灭全人类的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的你 还能保持理智吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个方案很硬来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只有你能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我能想到的 解救能力者的唯一方案
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 我没打算说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.25,0:15:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为了救步未妹妹 不惜穿越时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还来救过我和熊耳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾以为你只是个作弊狂魔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在 我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,评价变了好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 这个方案太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试试
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 这太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欠你一份情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你说只能这么做 我就做做看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动机好单纯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那种事可能再次发生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次 换我来救你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥意思？爱慕吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是爱慕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一脸认真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得做过什么让你有好感的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前说过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在另一个世界里 我变得自弃而堕落
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 是你一直陪在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…恐怕是我想负起责任来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我因此而得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么能扯到爱慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱不需要理由吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？阐述理由的明明是你吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 我们简直八字不合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我就是喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您还真是特别
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我送你一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我等你」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？等什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你解救所有能力者 等你再来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到那时 我们就做恋人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太看得起我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:17:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道很难做到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以当你做到时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会无条件地喜欢上乙坂有宇这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗬 那还真是不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有动力了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言为定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎的家伙扭手指
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉钩钩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后果真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比吞千根针要好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 从我开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.52,0:18:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要见一个能力者夺一个能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…我要做的 就是这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 我就变回正常人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会夺走世上的所有能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解救能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到的 放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是最强的能力者啊 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让熊耳白白牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有他在身边 我得到了多少救赎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.56,0:19:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而我却没机会向他道谢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才要去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.47,0:19:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让我珍爱的人变得不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去熊耳的哥哥 应该也是这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经夺走了友利的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:19:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺走？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动已经开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会退却的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个决定可不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…该怎么寻找能力者呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织的头目身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该都会有熊耳那样的能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则无法在短时间内
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招揽大量的能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有宇 飞出国门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本这边有我们在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然失去了熊耳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们依然是个统领能力者的大组织
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会支撑到能力消失之时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则 我也没脸去见那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有宇 你现在16岁是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赶在能力消失前办完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听友利同学说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我们的能力也拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会有点用的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹的也拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退场也要退得有味道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你可不能犹豫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 乙坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我收下三位的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.98,0:21:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…做什么的来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲同学 我这里有封令姐的信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和学生会的一伙人玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能永远在一起该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有件事让我很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲 虽然我一直和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.15,0:21:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却没能面对你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.26,0:22:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.26,0:22:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 死人要有死人的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美砂 书
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.87,0:22:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她 一直都和大家在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙坂同学 你一定要回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们同病相怜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.76,0:22:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起痛苦过 一起度过高中生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.92,0:22:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.07,0:22:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.59,0:22:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.26,0:22:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}带上这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}现在的我 只能做这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.27,0:23:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.33,0:23:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}有了这个 应该能勉强交流吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}花了一晚上做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}你的学习水平 我可清楚得很
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}是啊 作弊狂魔的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.80,0:23:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}那么 作为交换
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}帮我保管这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.16,0:23:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}我帮你保管一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}担心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.78,0:23:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}担心的事有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.36,0:23:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}但我必须去做
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}因为只有我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}那么 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs68\pos(960,1070)}嗯 一路顺风
